Invocation Name: viable
des: Viable is designed to help users discover the “viability,” or availability, of their startup, app, business, or product name. Start by saying, “Alexa, open Viable.” After the instructions, say the name of your prospective business (Taylor’s Tots, for example) and Viable will return the entry’s viability score based on domain availability, trademarks, comparable products, and more. You'll receive a score between 0 and 100, the higher the better! You can also use the Viable mobile app on your iOS device! Head to viable.af to download the app.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
